title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 14-9.26 - Superheater drains
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 14-9.26 - Superheater drains

State Regulations

Each superheater shall be equipped with at least one
drain so located as to most effectively provide for the proper operation of the
apparatus. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12
§§
14-9.26

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
